.. _readthedocs.io: http://hicexplorer.readthedocs.io/en/latest/index.html
.. _`Lieberman-Aiden et al. (2009)`: https://doi.org/10.1126%2Fscience.1181369
]]></help>
    <expand macro="citations" />
</tool>
